I watched your career from afar, hoping to run into you again some day, but our paths never crossed again.  Us haflin clerics are rare, and I like to know what ye all are doing.  Now that you are a filthy troll animal, though, I can't have nothin ta do with ye now.  Was the same way with Yugisha, way back when... a halfling cleric that then decided to be a lizard necromancer.  Such a shame to see so many once-good players turn to evil because that team has a bigger presence on our server.<br>
<br>
I continue to act as though there were alignments and racial tensions, and I absolutely do not believe in the myth of evil druids and good tier'dal.  Go ahead and spout your nonsense at me, all day long, I will not believe a word of it, and I will probably smash in your head if you bother me long enough.  At this point in my old age, I am playing my character more &quot;good&quot; than I initially meant for her to be, but this is because far too many people will compromise their characters' viewpoints and group with whatever is convenient.  <br>
